Package: skeletor
Type: Package
Title: Another R Package Skeleton Generator
Description: A tool for bootstrapping new packages with useful defaults, a test suite outline that passes checks, and helpers for adding documentation and running tests, both locally and on Travis-CI.
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2016-12-14
Authors@R: c(person("Neal", "Richardson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "neal.p.richardson@gmail.com"))
